  "detailed_description": "Cyberwinter is an isometric action strategy game. On a distant planet with a harsh climate, you have to fight legions of dangerous monsters for a new home for humanity. Build bases, develop and defend them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Enjoy an interesting story.</strong> Unravel the mystery of a lost civilization and determine the fate of the future;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/b6d2d12dd3daed5727e9875f7e7ffbf6.poster.avif?t=1624465021\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/b6d2d12dd3daed5727e9875f7e7ffbf6.webm?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/b6d2d12dd3daed5727e9875f7e7ffbf6.mp4?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Think, and only then do.</strong> Resources are extremely limited, build only what you really need;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/19c2a540a8fadaad2b3a1f0fe07b71fd.poster.avif?t=1624465021\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/19c2a540a8fadaad2b3a1f0fe07b71fd.webm?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/19c2a540a8fadaad2b3a1f0fe07b71fd.mp4?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Defeat the strongest.</strong> Thick and dangerous enemies will make your palms sweat;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/820136efa63d34dc415d3c465f870943.poster.avif?t=1624465021\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/820136efa63d34dc415d3c465f870943.webm?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/820136efa63d34dc415d3c465f870943.mp4?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Control the power.</strong> A variety of combat vehicles will make your gaming experience even more interesting.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/4bb7cebf84854115ae242e11ebcab60c.poster.avif?t=1624465021\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/4bb7cebf84854115ae242e11ebcab60c.webm?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425030/extras/4bb7cebf84854115ae242e11ebcab60c.mp4?t=1624465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
